---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Marquee from "../components/Marquee.astro";
---

<Layout>
  <main class="w-full flex flex-col lg:gap-24 gap-8 lg:mb-36">
    <span
      class="w-full flex items-center justify-center text-header lg:text-6xl text-4xl font-bold text-center text-primary tracking-wider mt-8"
      >We are SproutJourney</span
    >

    <div class="lg:text-4xl text-xl font-body text-center">
      At SproutJourney, it's not just about technologyâ€”it's about using AI to
      transform the way children learn. We're passionate, purpose-driven, and
      bold enough to explore groundbreaking ideas. If you're eager to make a
      real-world impact through cutting-edge AI in education, this is the place
      for you.
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-col gap-12">
      <span
        class="w-full flex items-center justify-center text-header lg:text-5xl text-3xl font-bold text-primary tracking-wider mt-8"
        >What is SproutJourney</span
      >

      <div class="flex lg:flex-row flex-col gap-12 justify-around">
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-2">
          <img src="/growth.svg" alt="" class="lg:w-36 lg:h-36 w-24 h-24" />
          <span class="text-xl font-bold font-body">Exponential Growth</span>
          <span class="text-lg font-body w-[50%] text-center"
            >Develop your skills in an environment that fosters innovation and
            collaboration.</span
          >
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-2">
          <img src="/inclusion.svg" alt="" class="lg:w-36 lg:h-36 w-24 h-24" />
          <span class="text-xl font-bold font-body">Open and Inclusive</span>
          <span class="text-lg font-body w-[50%] text-center"
            >We believe in the freedom to explore, fail, and rise stronger
            together.</span
          >
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-2">
          <img
            src="/inspiration.svg"
            alt=""
            class="lg:w-36 lg:h-36 w-24 h-24"
          />
          <span class="text-xl font-bold font-body">Inspiring People</span>
          <span class="text-lg font-body w-[50%] text-center"
            >Work alongside a team that challenges and motivates you every day.</span
          >
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <span
      class="w-full flex items-center justify-center text-header lg:text-5xl text-3xl font-bold text-primary tracking-wider mt-8"
      >Meet The Team</span
    >
    <Marquee />

    <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-full" >
      <a href="/contact" class="border-2 border-primary py-2 px-12 w-fit text-2xl"
        >Join Us</a
      >
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
